{"tid":1692610,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今晩2000民間記者會要人! 公務員齊聲反抗！","createTime":"2019-11-04T07:15:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T08:37:16.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f74e21c442fb7912e540f3338cc852c21e5cd19e","tid":1692610,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:15:41.000Z","msg":"第二十三次民間記者會<br />\n<br />\n數月以來，魔警假借「維護法紀」之名欺壓巿民，勾結鄉黑，視法制為無物。香港警隊樂於淪為政治工具，挾勢弄權，身為公僕卻與民為敵，更以暴力打壓香港言論及集會自由，干預區議會選舉。有化驗團隊亦發現，國產催淚彈的山埃含量超標，魔警恣意毒害市民。一眾有良知的公僕不齒魔警與極權政府的惡行，恥與為伍！數個公務員部門朋友率先現身民間記者會，齊聲反抗！<br />\n<br />\n主題：魔警濫權，人神共憤；公僕同僚，恥與為伍<br />\n日期：2019年11月4日（星期一）<br />\n時間：晚上8:00<br />\n<br />\n大家可於以下或其他頻道收看直播：<br />\n基進報導：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/radicalhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fradicalhk%2F&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfvrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=a78ab15c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/radicalhk/</a><br />\n反送中直播：<a href=\"http://www.hklivegroup.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hklivegroup.com%2F&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfvrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=7cde30b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hklivegroup.com/</a> （首次觀睇需要下載加密插件）<br />\n立場新聞：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2F&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfvrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=3d00351b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/</a><br />\n香港蘋果日報：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2F&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfvrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=22e2b3de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/</a><br />\n香港電台：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHKVNEWS%2F&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfvr